comments: Towns (MIN) grasps and releases Jokic?s (DEN) jersey and the marginal hold does not affect the latter?s FOM.
Barton (DEN) moves laterally along the path of Edwards (MIN) and the marginal arm to the offensive player's side does not impact his SQBR.
Beverley (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (DEN) and some marginal contact occurs that does not alter Gordon's defensive play.
Morris (DEN) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Russell (MIN).
Towns (MIN) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm and affects his shot attempt at the rim.
Jokic (DEN) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Hyland (DEN) and Edwards (MIN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Russell (MIN) moves into Hyland's (DEN) extended off-arm as he makes a move on the perimeter but the contact is marginal.
Towns (MIN) legally contests Barton's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Hyland (DEN) reaches in and initiates contact to Prince (MIN) that affects his SQBR.
Jokic (DEN) extends his arms into Reid (MIN) during the screen and continues moving into him, affecting his ability to contest the shot.
Reed (DEN) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
Edwards (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Hyland (DEN) on the perimeter and Hyland loses control of the ball on his own.
